Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.98,0:00:08.40,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Time has really flown.  \NHas it already been three years?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.40,0:00:12.07,grave,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Wataya Family Grave
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.40,0:00:13.48,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I can still hear Master \NWataya's voice sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.32,0:00:17.22,Chiha-main,Dada,0000,0000,0000,,Arata, it's getting hot, \Nso let's head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.22,0:00:18.35,Chiha-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.35,0:00:20.70,Chiha-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I just put those sandwiches \Nthere as an offering.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.35,0:00:24.25,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand why Grandpa \Nand Dad never got along.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,0:00:26.28,Chiha-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Your grandpa didn't like me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.28,0:00:28.86,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,because I wasn't interested in karuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.86,0:00:30.88,Chiha-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Your quarrels were the reason you took
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.88,0:00:34.26,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,a job in Tokyo and forced \NArata to switch schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.48,0:00:35.97,Chiha-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,B-But!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.17,0:00:37.50,Chiha-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,It was a good experience, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.50,0:00:39.42,Chiha-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You made friends in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:45.37,Chiha-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.37,0:00:48.06,Chiha-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,The Tokyo High School \NRegional is today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.60,0:00:50.55,Chiha-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Are your friends doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.55,0:00:51.96,Chiha-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You exchange e-mails, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.96,0:00:53.54,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,No, not as often as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.89,0:00:56.05,Chiha-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You need to send more e-mails
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.05,0:00:59.49,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,or your friends in Tokyo \Nwill forget about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.49,0:01:02.08,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Really?  I doubt that would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.09,0:01:04.97,Chiha-flashback,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Cell phones are incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.40,0:01:06.79,Chiha-flashback,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Like the misty bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.71,0:01:13.62,Chiha-internal,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.33,0:01:16.95,Chiha-internal,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,In my mind, our misty bridge...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.44,0:01:19.35,Chiha-internal,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,is not a cell phone, but something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.47,0:01:23.02,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.73,0:01:27.63,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,If I win the National High \NSchool Championship,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.13,0:01:29.50,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to grant my request.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.61,0:01:43.04,Chiha-title2,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1800)}Chihaya Furu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.09,0:02:45.60,Chiha-ep-title-verse,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}Verse 4
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.09,0:02:45.60,Chiha-ep-title-poem-wide,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}To tell the \Npeople in \Nthe capital \Nthat I make \Nfor the \Nislands
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.55,0:02:43.88,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.88,0:02:46.06,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we don't miss the finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:49.31,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,They should have made it \N past the prelim stage, easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.58,0:02:51.03,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.03,0:02:54.49,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Mashima-kun hasn't sent any \Ne-mails about them losing yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.86,0:02:56.56,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Eyebrows...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:03:00.53,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what his problem is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:04.72,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Based on his play during practice, \Nhe should be a Class A player now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.30,0:03:09.12,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,He's put in so much effort, \Nso why can't he win a tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.17,0:03:12.43,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, I ran into
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.43,0:03:15.53,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mashima-kun at the Kyoto \Nand Hiroshima tournaments
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.53,0:03:17.12,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,and watched him play.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.47,0:03:18.76,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.59,0:03:21.45,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,...he just has terrible luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:25.56,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,He can never catch a lucky break \Nwhen he needs it the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:28.49,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Mashima-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:31.48,made,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,I made them                    myself <3
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:30.90,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Please, have some!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.63,0:03:35.11,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I try to avoid eating \Nanything solid before a match.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:38.61,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. Mashima, you're \Ncopying Dr. Harada?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.91,0:03:40.03,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:43.04,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,If we win our next match, \Nwe're in the Nationals!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.04,0:03:44.68,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,You can have some, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.68,0:03:45.62,Chiha-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:49.25,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.05,0:03:52.58,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,If I lose after doing everything \NI can, I can accept that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:56.34,prelims-1,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Group C Preliminary
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.36,0:03:55.79,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,What's important is that I do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:58.25,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.60,0:03:59.66,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Harada!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.66,0:04:01.28,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like you're doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.28,0:04:02.90,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:05.18,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for coming to cheer us—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.01,0:04:12.10,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm certainly here to cheer you on,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:14.25,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,but that's not the only \Nreason I'm here this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:17.48,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,It's twice as exciting for me, \Nbut also quite distressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.85,0:04:18.48,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:21.49,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?  Haven't you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.83,0:04:22.74,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.74,0:04:23.82,sup?,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,1)}Homei
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.04,0:04:23.82,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:26.70,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,The team to defeat last year's \Ndark horse, Mizusawa,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:29.06,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,will be this year's dark horse, Homei!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.06,0:04:29.83,Chiha-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.19,0:04:31.75,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuboguchi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:34.25,Regional,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,High School Championship Tokyo Regional Final \NTournament Bracket
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:34.25,prelims-2,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Mizusawa High\N\NHomei High\N\NHokuo Academy\N\NShoyo High
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:34.25,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,This could be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.41,0:04:36.94,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they were \Ncompletely off my radar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.94,0:04:39.64,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,The data from last year won't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.86,0:04:39.64,Chiha-overlap,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.12,0:04:42.21,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Homei's advisor, Tsuboguchi-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.56,0:04:45.72,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,was the East Representative for \Nthe Master match last year,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:49.35,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,and he's the ace of the Shiranami society \NChihaya-chan and the president are in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:51.18,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know, Chihaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:57.69,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand what \Ngets you excited...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:05:00.07,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's worked hard \Nto make it this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.55,0:05:02.94,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,You're playing much better than two \Nmonths of practice can account for!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:14.58,count,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Every Card Counts
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:05.86,Chiha-main,Take,0000,0000,0000,,Your advice was spot on, Coach!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:09.02,Chiha-main,Toda,0000,0000,0000,,After changing my form, \Nmy swing is much smoother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.02,0:05:10.24,Chiha-main,Nana,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:12.51,Chiha-main,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,I followed your instructions \Nfor sending cards
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.51,0:05:14.58,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and my opponent made four mistakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.74,0:05:17.31,Chiha-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Lost that one, lost that \None, lost that one...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.31,0:05:20.15,Chiha-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,"I hear," "As this," "Note that," \N"The storm blasts," "May it"...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.15,0:05:22.42,Chiha-overlap,Take,0000,0000,0000,,Sasa, you need to learn to let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.15,0:05:22.43,Chiha-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,"My fear is not," "The autumn wind," "Like the"...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.13,0:05:26.64,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Mizusawa is strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.64,0:05:31.59,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,but the practice and hard work you've \Nput in since spring will pay off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:36.39,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Will you take me to Omi Jingu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.70,0:05:37.46,Chiha-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:40.95,Chiha-internal,All,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's youthful spirit...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.58,0:05:45.40,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,They changed orders every match.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.88,0:05:47.04,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to see any patterns.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.96,0:05:52.11,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Go easy on us, reigning champions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.26,0:05:59.17,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I've known Tsuboguchi-san \Nsince I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.30,0:06:02.19,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,He wants to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.99,0:06:04.51,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,What order will they use?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:06.33,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Who's their strongest player?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.33,0:06:08.88,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,What order do we use to \Nguarantee three victories?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.88,0:06:10.14,gl,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Good Luck
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.88,0:06:10.49,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi-kun!  Taichi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:12.93,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!  I bought this for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:14.01,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,A lucky charm!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.01,0:06:15.60,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I bought one, too!  Take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:17.70,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,All you're missing is the luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.70,0:06:19.10,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,You have the skill!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.61,0:06:21.61,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I need to come \Nup with our order!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:26.11,Chiha-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Will the semifinalists please \Nturn in their orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.72,0:06:28.24,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, there's no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.34,0:06:33.48,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Eyebrows...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.48,0:06:35.32,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,An individual match is a team match.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:38.37,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,A team match is an individual match.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.37,0:06:43.49,Chiha-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Homei High School, Takei-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:46.04,Chiha-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Mizusawa High School, Komano-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.53,0:06:46.04,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,What did he mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.62,0:06:49.17,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Homei High School, Toda-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.62,0:06:50.63,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Team matches and individual \Nmatches are different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.17,0:06:52.04,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Mizusawa High School, Mashima-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:55.06,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,The side that does better \Nas a team will win!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.04,0:06:55.06,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Homei High School, Sasa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:57.56,Chiha-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Please begin placing your cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.92,0:07:01.15,Chiha-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,After a fifteen minute memorization \Nperiod, the match will begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.95,0:07:03.06,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.87,0:07:07.57,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Group C had strong schools like Kase \NHigh and Eiko University High.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.21,0:07:10.49,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,They must have improved a lot \Nwith Tsuboguchi-san's teaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.93,0:07:12.11,Chiha-main,Take,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.71,0:07:14.79,Chiha-main,Take,0000,0000,0000,,You're totally my type!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.79,0:07:16.58,Chiha-main,Take,0000,0000,0000,,Give me your number after the match!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:18.50,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:19.12,Chiha-internal,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:22.16,Chiha-internal,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya-chan isn't used \Nto romantic stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.16,0:07:22.88,Chiha-internal,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,so we can use that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.53,0:07:25.07,Chiha-internal,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I know that she'll go back
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.07,0:07:27.59,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,to being crazy about karuta \Nonce the match starts,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:30.38,Chiha-internal,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,so we're only pretending \Nto go after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:31.73,Chiha-main,Take,0000,0000,0000,,So how about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.73,0:07:32.51,Chiha-main,Take,0000,0000,0000,,It's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:34.89,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do?  What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.37,0:07:36.47,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,That's dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:38.72,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,You're taking advantage \Nof Chihaya's personality!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:41.60,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I know what you're up \Nto, Tsuboguchi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.17,0:07:44.34,Chiha-internal,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,In reality, we're throwing \NEyebrows off his game.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.34,0:07:46.31,Chiha-internal,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya-chan may be Mizusawa's ace,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.31,0:07:48.58,Chiha-internal,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,but Eyebrows is their mental leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:51.95,Chiha-internal,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,You pay too much attention \Nto your surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.59,0:07:55.26,Chiha-internal,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure that you \Nshould be glaring at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:57.37,Chiha-main,Mochi,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Harada.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:07:58.81,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mochida-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.81,0:08:01.21,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like Hokuo is \Nwinning their games.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.49,0:08:03.09,Chiha-main,Mochi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:05.80,Chiha-main,Mochi,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, did you notice, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:11.62,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Naniwa Bay, now the flower \Nblooms, but for winter
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.41,0:08:09.40,Chiha-main,Mochi,0000,0000,0000,,They're switching readers \Nevery round this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:11.98,Chiha-main,Mochi,0000,0000,0000,,It must have been difficult \Nto find five readers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.98,0:08:13.96,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.96,0:08:15.25,Chiha-main,Mochi,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.96,0:08:20.51,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Here comes spring,\N now the flower blooms
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.28,0:08:32.50,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes spring, now \Nthe flower blooms
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:43.66,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,My life means nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:45.30,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,What was that pause about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:47.11,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Mochida-kun, is he an amateur?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.11,0:08:49.42,Chiha-main,Mochi,0000,0000,0000,,No, Tashiro-kun is certified!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:54.05,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,...to see you again
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.05,0:08:55.69,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could show the...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.69,0:08:57.02,Chiha-internal,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't wait long enough this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.02,0:08:59.72,Chiha-internal,Mochi,0000,0000,0000,,Tashiro-kun's nervous because he was
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:00.93,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,just certified as a Class B reader!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:03.68,Chiha-internal,Mochi,0000,0000,0000,,He's not following the correct rhythm!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.88,0:09:05.31,Chiha-internal,A,0000,0000,0000,,Mizusawa's at a disadvantage!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:08.11,Chiha-internal,A,0000,0000,0000,,The strange rhythm will affect \Nexperienced players more!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:09.73,Chiha-internal,B,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi-kun's luck is so terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.25,0:09:14.39,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Karuta is similar to dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.39,0:09:20.45,irritated,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,100)}Irritated\NIrritated\NIrritated\NIrritated
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.29,0:09:19.31,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,You can't dance if the \Nmusic is off beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:20.53,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Oe-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.28,0:09:22.48,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Focus on the first card.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.48,0:09:23.58,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Make your own rhythm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.81,0:09:27.58,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.86,0:09:33.04,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,...with tears of blood
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.89,0:09:35.72,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,A mountain village grows...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:39.05,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya and Nishida are fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:40.35,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,What about Komano?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.75,0:09:42.50,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Komano, attack the next card!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:43.31,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.03,0:09:47.24,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,My opponent's card \Nplacement is very familiar,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.24,0:09:48.71,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,since their coach is Tsuboguchi-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.32,0:09:51.28,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,and he's playing the Shiranami \Noffensive karuta style.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.80,0:09:53.15,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Offensive is my style, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:56.34,Chiha-main,Take,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love a girlfriend \Nwho's good at karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.34,0:09:57.32,Chiha-main,Take,0000,0000,0000,,You're perfe—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:10:00.45,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Focus on the opponent's \Nbottom right side!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:02.45,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,I feel that my love...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:06.46,Chiha-internal,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya-chan's gotten better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:11.54,Chiha-internal,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected to defeat the \Ntwo Class A Mizusawa players.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.07,0:10:13.88,Chiha-internal,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.88,0:10:17.20,Chiha-main,Take,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!  I took one from \Nmy opponent's side!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.20,0:10:17.75,Chiha-main,Nana,0000,0000,0000,,Same here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.75,0:10:18.63,Chiha-main,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,Good, keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:24.02,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,He's taking all the \Ncards I'm not watching,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:25.96,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,while sending all the cards \NI've been targeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.91,0:10:30.30,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuboguchi-san's taught \Nthem all the nasty tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.87,0:10:32.91,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,A mountain stream dips...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.23,0:10:35.84,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, I was too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:38.20,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I need to focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:45.14,Chiha-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!  Come on!  Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.14,0:10:47.70,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure I want to ignore that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.85,0:10:51.08,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody wishes to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.65,0:10:51.08,Chiha-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it would come!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.22,0:10:56.21,Chiha-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!  Come on!  Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.08,0:10:56.21,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Some kind of curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:10:58.98,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:00.88,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,She's the only one acting so strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:05.51,Chiha-internal,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,I've dreamed about becoming the karuta \Nqueen since I was a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.62,0:11:09.90,Chiha-internal,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,However, I didn't have the courage \Nto enter a karuta society,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.90,0:11:13.00,Chiha-internal,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,so I had to practice and work \Non my positioning by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.71,0:11:15.52,Chiha-internal,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Our high school had a karuta club,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:17.08,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,but they just sat around chatting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.95,0:11:21.59,Chiha-internal,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,That was when my savior arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:24.69,Chiha-flashback,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, karuta is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.69,0:11:25.90,Chiha-flashback,All,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:28.70,Chiha-flashback,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's not karuta that's fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.90,0:11:33.89,Chiha-flashback,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,It's the act of trying \Nyour hardest that's fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.62,0:11:36.88,Chiha-internal,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,I was shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.73,0:11:43.05,Chiha-internal,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't the only one \Nwho wanted to try hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.25,0:11:45.53,Chiha-internal,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,I was shocked...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.07,0:11:50.43,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,The sky may hold...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:50.43,Chiha-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,It came!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.76,0:11:52.06,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,She guessed two cards in a row?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.06,0:11:54.26,Chiha-internal,B,0000,0000,0000,,He's trying to attack, but \Nhe's not getting any chances!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.26,0:11:55.02,Chiha-internal,A,0000,0000,0000,,Horrible luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.05,0:11:58.23,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,So spring ends...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:11:57.97,Chiha-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:05.46,Chiha-internal,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Eyebrows doesn't believe \Nthat he just needs luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.83,0:12:09.33,Chiha-internal,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,He continues to believe \Nthat he lacks the skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.49,0:12:11.33,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:14.70,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,She can guess cards this \Nwell after two months
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.70,0:12:16.77,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,of instruction from Tsuboguchi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.46,0:12:19.34,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I've been working my ass off for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:24.08,Chiha-internal,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,But when he tells himself that \Nit's skill that he lacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.72,0:12:27.99,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Her sense is better than mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:30.14,Chiha-internal,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,he falls victim
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.30,0:12:35.56,Chiha-internal,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,to the belief that he \Ndoesn't have the talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.41,0:12:42.03,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because of the reader's rhythm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.43,0:12:44.33,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't leading the way \Nwe were in the prelims.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.04,0:12:45.95,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,What about Nishida?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.90,0:12:48.38,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,He's up by ten cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.38,0:12:49.45,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:50.68,Chiha-flashback,Retro,0000,0000,0000,,Porky.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.68,0:12:52.45,Chiha-flashback,Retro,0000,0000,0000,,You're too nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:55.41,Chiha-flashback,Retro,0000,0000,0000,,Why let Mashima, who's stuck \Nin Class B even though
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.41,0:12:57.08,Chiha-flashback,Retro,0000,0000,0000,,he tops you all in skill, be your president?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.66,0:13:00.40,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Stuck in Class B...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.06,0:13:04.64,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Which card is she aiming for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.23,0:13:07.09,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Check the card she just sent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:08.35,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Talent...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.22,0:13:10.65,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,She's watching "When the,"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.65,0:13:13.18,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,but being careful since the empty card \N"When I" hasn't been read yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.58,0:13:14.44,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Talent...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.44,0:13:16.40,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,"When winds blow" and "When winds \Nsend" are still out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.99,0:13:17.90,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Talent...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.92,0:13:20.77,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,This won't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:22.98,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Focus!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:26.34,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Refresh my memory! Check everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.81,0:13:27.57,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:30.74,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,The air conditioner above \NTaichi-kun isn't working.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:33.15,Chiha-internal,B,0000,0000,0000,,Why now?!  Why that one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.15,0:13:33.87,Chiha-internal,A,0000,0000,0000,,Horrible luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:36.20,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hot...  I need a towel...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.13,0:13:43.38,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,My memorization...  My hard work...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.38,0:13:45.51,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,The emotions experienced...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.96,0:13:45.51,Chiha-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:48.32,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't doing anything for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.28,0:13:51.34,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,This is a good match.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.34,0:13:53.97,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Eyebrows is up against \Na strong opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:57.49,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she's hooked on your teachings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.61,0:14:01.50,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,"Play like you can guess \Nwhat card's coming next."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.50,0:14:02.82,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,"If you end up taking a different card,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:06.37,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,talk like it was the \None you were expecting."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:09.30,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of birds crossing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.30,0:14:10.99,Chiha-internal,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about that card.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.29,0:14:13.99,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,It's a simple strategy,\Nbut it's not easy to pull off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.66,0:14:16.70,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,If she can convince him that the flow
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.70,0:14:19.00,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,is on her side, and not on his,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:22.21,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,she might be able to overwhelm him while \Nhe's worried about leading the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:26.29,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty passionate about this,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.29,0:14:29.09,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,considering that you're the biggest \NClass A slacker in our society.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.92,0:14:35.14,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,I had to ignore my own problems...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:37.65,Chiha-internal,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,It's the act of trying \Nyour hardest that's fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.29,0:14:39.62,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,...to inspire them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:43.77,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't try my hardest,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.69,0:14:46.52,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,so I was left with regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:55.49,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Every match is close, and it's so hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.46,0:15:00.75,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,What do I have to do to become \NMashima-senpai's girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:02.63,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!  What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.07,0:15:06.49,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing else for me to \Ndo right now besides think.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:07.01,lovestruck,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1)}She's \Nreally\Ncrazy \Nabout \Nlove...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.67,0:15:10.07,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,After watching him for two \Nmonths, it's become very clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.07,0:15:13.01,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Mashima-senpai is in \Nlove with Ayase-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.11,0:15:14.93,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.34,0:15:18.52,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase-senpai doesn't pay any \Nattention to Mashima-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.02,0:15:22.21,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.21,0:15:23.75,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,The air conditioner in the very back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.75,0:15:25.90,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Can I start after this match is over?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.22,0:15:33.47,Chiha-internal,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,It's a sauna!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.47,0:15:34.74,Chiha-internal,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, it's only affecting my kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:37.31,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,This sweat feels gross...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.37,0:15:40.61,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to wipe it off \Nwith a loaner kimono,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.56,0:15:42.91,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't have a towel...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.91,0:15:44.50,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,As I wait for...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:45.58,Chiha-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.58,0:15:46.54,Chiha-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Go on the attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.54,0:15:47.35,Chiha-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.71,0:15:53.93,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.28,0:15:55.24,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Can I have a towel?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.35,0:16:24.54,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:28.09,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I always try to play it cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.39,0:16:31.03,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I feel embarrassed about losing,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.49,0:16:34.48,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,so I run off to tournaments \Nfar away in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.46,0:16:38.60,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I know that I'm not alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.46,0:16:41.10,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.89,0:16:46.85,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be strong, even when I'm alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:56.02,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,my body burns like the seaweed \Ndrying on the shores of Matsuho
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:16:57.85,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,The storm will soon carry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.17,0:17:02.25,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's one card!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.93,0:17:06.66,Chiha-internal,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,He's keeping his eyes on \Nthe cards while speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:09.00,Chiha-internal,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,He's not turning to look \Nat his teammates.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.60,0:17:11.26,Chiha-internal,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Eyebrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.34,0:17:14.06,Chiha-internal,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,A team match is an individual match.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.84,0:17:17.56,Chiha-internal,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,You must trust in your teammates \Nwhile playing by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.99,0:17:23.77,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:25.81,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,To watch the other match.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.81,0:17:27.83,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,I can scout out our \Nopponent in the finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:32.31,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,"There's nothing else to do \Nright now besides think"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.74,0:17:33.78,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,There has to be something else!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.94,0:17:38.46,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a member of this team!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.80,0:17:41.58,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,A member of the Mizusawa karuta club!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.44,0:17:49.35,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,No matter where I stand \Non the shores of Tago,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.28,0:17:52.55,Chiha-main,Rieko,0000,0000,0000,,He caught up!
