Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:22.62,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,The hazy early morning \Nlight comes not from...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.02,0:18:25.48,Chiha-internal,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,He's built a lead in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.17,0:18:28.66,Chiha-internal,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,She was able to make her sense \Nwork in the first half,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.05,0:18:30.06,Chiha-internal,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,but in the second half...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:32.13,Chiha-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm moving my cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:35.79,Chiha-internal,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring them together \Nand hit them all together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.38,0:18:38.09,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Waves creep closer...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.09,0:18:39.51,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Feel sorrow wash over me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.79,0:18:41.41,Chiha-internal,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not giving up yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.41,0:18:42.51,Chiha-internal,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,I want to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:45.02,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,1 to 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:48.09,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,He just needs one more card, but the cards \Nhave all been on his opponent's side!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.09,0:18:49.65,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,His luck is still horrible!
