Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.67,0:19:46.00,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Did everyone win?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:47.58,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,What's the score?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.20,0:19:50.26,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.26,0:19:54.10,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a failure as the president \Nif I don't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:55.92,Chiha-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.31,0:19:58.68,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.70,0:20:01.07,Chiha-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry, Coach!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.07,0:20:03.18,Chiha-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,My dedication wasn't strong enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.41,0:20:07.85,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Eyebrows, how many cards were left?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.52,0:20:10.58,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,95 cards were read,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.58,0:20:12.21,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,so there were only 5 cards left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.21,0:20:13.48,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,None of them were empty cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.87,0:20:13.48,creepy,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,What?!       \NHe knew that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.65,0:20:14.65,creepy2,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,What?!       \NHe knew that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.30,0:20:18.80,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,The last card had become \Na first-syllable card,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.80,0:20:20.40,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but you didn't move fast enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.02,0:20:24.05,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,because you thought there might \Nbe other {\i1}The{\i0} cards left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.05,0:20:26.22,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,You lost your lead in the second \Nhalf because your opponent
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.22,0:20:27.76,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,was more aware of how \Nmany cards were left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.28,0:20:30.99,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it creepy when someone \Ncan memorize cards like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.44,0:20:33.67,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,He practices like crazy every day,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.81,0:20:38.84,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm inspired by the \Neffort he puts in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.52,0:20:41.51,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.82,0:20:43.65,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wash these towels \Nbefore returning them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.65,0:20:44.93,Chiha-main,Rieko,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, Taichi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.17,0:20:46.91,Chiha-main,Rieko,0000,0000,0000,,It's because the air \Nconditioning wasn't working!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.91,0:20:48.69,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,You can have all the towels you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.69,0:20:50.14,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck in your next match.
