Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.82,0:20:57.46,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you too, Hanano-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.46,0:20:58.47,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.77,0:21:02.03,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,I have to be on my guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.76,0:21:05.94,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase-senpai is watching \NMashima-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.99,0:21:09.61,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Though, I can't be entirely sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.53,0:21:14.20,prelims-3,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizusawa High\N\NHomei High\N\NHokuo Academy\N\NShoyo High
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.26,0:21:19.50,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Our next match is against the \Nstrongest school in Tokyo, Hokuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.23,0:21:23.74,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,They'll give us their best shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.33,0:21:25.59,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,We have to play to win!
